import React from 'react'
import { ReactNavbar } from 'overlay-navbar'
import logo from '../../images/logo.png'
function Header() {
    return (
        <ReactNavbar
            burgerColor="#eb4034"
            burgerColorHover="#a62d4"
            logo={logo}
            logoWidth="500px"
            navColor1="purplish"
            nav1Text="Your shopping destination"
            logoHoverSize="100px"
            link1Text="Home"
            link2Text="Product"
            link3Text="Contact"
            link4Text="About"

            link1Url="/home"
            link2Url="/product"
            link3Url="/contact"
            link4Url="/about"
            link1Size="1.2vmax"
            link1Color="rgba(35,35,25,0.8)"
            nav2justifyContent="flex-end"
            nav3justifyContent="flex-start"

            link1ColorHover="#eb4034"
            link2ColorHover="#eb4034"
            link3ColorHover="#eb4034"
            link4ColorHover="#eb4034"

            link1Margin="2vmax"
            link2Margin="6vmax"
            link3Margin="1vmax"
            link4Margin="10vmax"




        />
    )
}

export default Header;
